# Suckless Youtube - Firefox extention

## Idea pipeline
- UI button which lets you start download
    - HTML & JS
    - Web socket
        -> Start download
        <- Status of current download
        - Queue
    - youtube-dl backend
    - opens in a player
        - VLC
            - python-vlc

## Two components

### Firefox extension

- Hooks Youtube's UI
- Monitors downloads from backend


### Backend

- Python script
- Handles download(s)
- Communicates progress
